Describe how to install it

	apt-get install mpg321
	apt-get install vorbis-tools

Compile from source
===================

Debian:
	apt-get install build-essential
	apt-get install libc6-dev
	apt-get install libncurses5-dev
	apt-get install libvorbis-dev
	apt-get install libflac-dev
	apt-get install libfcgi-dev

NetBSD:	
	-I/usr/pkg/include -L/usr/pkg/lib  -Wl,-R/usr/pkg/lib
	pkg_add ncurses
	pkg_add libvorbis
	pkg_add flac

FreeBSD:
	-I/usr/local/include -L/usr/local/lib
	
$ make
$ sudo make install
	
MacOSX: (10.4 or later required)
    Install Apple's developertools, from cd or internet.
    Install macports (http://www.macports.org/)
    sudo port -vd install libogg libvorbis flac mpg321
    sudo port -vd install vorbis-tools +player +flac +speex
    
    In sources directory run:
    $ xcodebuild





